{"type":"message","id":"b355714d","parentId":"aea40f05","timestamp":"2026-06-16T15:16:06.140Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a10zlsha8qtz_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"* 查询Tiktok平台产品详情\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n  function tiktok_product_detail(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"TH\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\" | \"JP\");\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品趋势，同时返回`销量`，`价格`，`星级`，`评论数量`，`新增带货视频数`，`新增带货达人数`多个维度\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n  function tiktok_product_trend(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"TH\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\" | \"JP\");\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品的带货达人\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n  function tiktok_product_video_author(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"TH\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\" | \"JP\");\n   * 查询产品在Tiktok平台上的相似产品，可用于分析此类产品的销售情况\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n  function tiktok_similar_product(productName: string, page?: number, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"TH\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\" | \"JP\");\n   * 通过1688平台找产品的采购货源。可用于分析产品的采购成本价\n  function ali1688_similar_product(searchName: string);\n  function similar_product_feature(productName: string, amzSite?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"GB\" | \"DE\" | \"FR\" | \"IN\" | \"CA\" | \"JP\" | \"ES\" | \"IT\" | \"MX\" | \"AE\" | \"AU\" | \"BR\" | \"SA\");\n   * 按名称搜索Tiktok平台上相关类目\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品的带货视频\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n  function tiktok_product_video(productId: string, page?: number, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"TH\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\" | \"JP\");"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2259,"aggregated":"* 查询Tiktok平台产品详情\n   * @param site? TikTok站点\n  function tiktok_product_detail(productId: string, site?: \"Unknow\" | \"US\" | \"MY\" | \"PH\" | \"VN\" | \"TH\" | \"ID\" | \"GB\" | \"JP\");\n   * 查询Tiktok平台产品趋势，同时返回`销量`，`价格`，`星级`，`评论数量`，`新增带货视频数`，`新增带货达人数`多个维度\n   *